channel.title: Solo Journey - Andrew Young
channel.description:
This track features some pianos, pads, and melodic percussion. I’ve put a pretty decent set of drums in the track as well. The end of the track has an ambient feel to it. Let me know what you think of this track!
https://soundcloud.com/andrewyoung300/solo-journey
